Arrêtez! Arrêtez!

934
02:07:12,655 --> 02:07:14,115
Aller.

935
02:07:16,617 --> 02:07:20,600
Continuez à avancer! En avant!

936
02:07:50,191 --> 02:07:51,111
Là.

937
02:08:13,213 --> 02:08:16,122
Joshua! Aaron!

938
02:08:31,314 --> 02:08:34,230
Courrez! Tout le monde, courrez!

939
02:08:34,609 --> 02:08:35,802
Aller!

940
02:08:35,902 --> 02:08:38,006
Vers la côte!

